WEBVTT

00:00.332 --> 00:01.865
It's nearly done.

00:02.059 --> 00:03.526
I want the real Rose back.

00:03.527 --> 00:06.025
You put her in harm's
way, then you judge her.

00:06.026 --> 00:07.958
Marriage is about family.

00:07.959 --> 00:09.659
There's no point doing it
if you can't have children.

00:09.660 --> 00:11.392
In the Catholic Church,

00:11.393 --> 00:14.192
annulment is possible
under certain conditions.

00:14.193 --> 00:15.626
You just saying all this to shock me?

00:15.627 --> 00:17.793
If we went to a tribunal,

00:17.794 --> 00:20.459
it wouldn't just be because
I can't have children.

00:20.460 --> 00:24.459
I knew before we were married,
and I kept it from you.

00:24.460 --> 00:26.459
You lied to me.

00:26.460 --> 00:30.325
Elizabeth Bligh, will you marry me?

00:30.326 --> 00:31.859
Yes.

00:31.860 --> 00:32.992
Yes, I will.

00:32.993 --> 00:36.492
Well, some months ago I
succumbed to blackmail,

00:36.493 --> 00:40.793
the very thing we all fear, and I caved.

00:40.794 --> 00:42.559
Who?

00:42.560 --> 00:43.925
Regina Bligh.

00:43.926 --> 00:46.958
Who is the father of the Nordmann child?

00:46.959 --> 00:50.126
The milkman or the
dustman for all we know.

00:51.527 --> 00:52.659
Or George Bligh.

00:52.660 --> 00:54.492
I can't afford to go down for this.

00:54.493 --> 00:58.592
You do not want to go back
to your stupid, stupid wife!

00:58.593 --> 01:00.225
Do you? Do...

01:00.226 --> 01:02.526
(HORSE NEIGHS)

01:02.527 --> 01:04.426
I was almost fooled
into killing someone.

01:04.427 --> 01:06.192
Who is it that wants me dead?

01:06.193 --> 01:07.459
Regina Bligh.

01:07.460 --> 01:09.025
Everything points towards Regina

01:09.026 --> 01:11.459
killing this young schoolteacher.

01:11.460 --> 01:14.159
One day she may stand trial,
but first things first,

01:14.160 --> 01:15.592
I want to deal with the
fact that she's...

01:15.593 --> 01:16.925
well, she's mentally unhinged.

01:16.926 --> 01:20.259
Yeah. No one needs to
know she's gone gaga.

01:20.260 --> 01:23.592
Jack's been most helpful
with these referrals.

01:23.593 --> 01:25.826
Riverview Hall is one of the best.

01:25.827 --> 01:27.359
Mrs. Bligh!

01:27.360 --> 01:28.925
Oh, my gosh, there are
people coming to get you.

01:28.926 --> 01:30.660
- Who?
- Doctors, I think.

01:32.993 --> 01:33.527
(THUD)

01:35.560 --> 01:36.493
DR. GRIFFIN: Where is she?

01:42.596 --> 01:45.909
